What is the solution of this equation?

\vspace{2mm}

\textbf{A}. 
$y=e^{-y}$

\textbf{B}. 
$y=e^{y}$

\textbf{C}. 
\bpycod
from math import exp
def f(x):
    return exp(x)
\epycod

