        \nabla\cdot\nabla\boldsymbol{u} = \nu\nabla^2\boldsymbol{u} -
        \frac{1}{\varrho}\nabla p,

and :math:`\nabla\boldsymbol{u} (\boldsymbol{x})\cdot\boldsymbol{n}`.

