<span style="color: #000080; font-weight: bold">In [3]: </span>y <span style="color: #666666">=</span> exp(<span style="color: #666666">-0.1*</span>x)<span style="color: #666666">*</span>sin(x)
<span style="color: #0044DD">---------------------------------------------------------------------------</span>
