  - subitem1 of item2
  - subitem2 of item2

 - item3

Note that sublists are consistently indented by one or more blanks as
shown: bullets must exactly match and continuation lines must start
right below the line above.

Here is an enumeration list:

1. item1
2. item2
   may appear on
   multiple lines
