Supported Formats
-----------------

DocOnce currently translates files to the following formats:

 * LaTeX (format latex and pdflatex)

 * HTML (format html)

 * reStructuredText (format rst)

 * plain (untagged) ASCII (format plain)

 * Sphinx (format sphinx)

